title: "GAN variations(DCGAN, CGAN, PGGAN and StyleGAN)에 대하여"
category: "ai papers"
publishedAt: "2022-12-11"
thumbnail: "https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/79881119/209126974-59cf4988-bf47-407a-8a36-df5bf70644a2.png"
